{"tid":224270,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"IMAX 3D眼鏡借用服務將提供至今年五月廿四日","createTime":"2017-05-01T02:16:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T10:22:40.000Z","uid":36164,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5bb59c6bd84f9422f5fd9a77e79fd98ec84af9f6","tid":224270,"uid":36164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T02:16:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkfilmblog.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/04/IMG_4025.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F04%2FIMG_4025.jpg&h=471ef308&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五月廿五日起每副正式為港幣二十元。<br />\n<br />\n如斯的做法，反映UA院線「歛財」方面不遺餘力，IMAX 3D影院戲院可適用戲院極少，但是卻要觀眾自行購買，而且售價更比一般3D眼鏡高出一截。相比之下，戲院便可減少眼鏡保養與清潔的成本。"},{"pid":"67494f0e48ba86cf11360a87eea3cd5131d8722f","tid":224270,"uid":36164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T02:17:36.000Z","msg":"可以罷睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母等執笠啦"},{"pid":"4d419c3e540e280107f188f67b60fdda8d2cca0e","tid":224270,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T02:18:06.000Z","msg":"會員又無折<br />\nUA睇死佢啲客唔會走？"},{"pid":"0a2e0993e7b5d4b458ca0bb7392cbe55f4b9dfdb","tid":224270,"uid":36164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T02:18:19.000Z","msg":"唔記得貼source<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/55429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F55429&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2gCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=669415b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/55429</a>"},{"pid":"08d9b8527716720adf1f871119ca77f39614916f","tid":224270,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T02:19:02.000Z","msg":"寧原買副"},{"pid":"6459b3a27ef35d87a3d4f9999fc1347a4f0dc02b","tid":224270,"uid":2959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T02:19:02.000Z","msg":"原來係同普通3d唔同<img sr